data.description: Here is your chance to own your own piece of paradise. Welcome to this stunning two-story home featuring 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and boasting a spacious 2152 square feet in the beautiful Willow Walk community.  This Maronda built  Lexington model is beautiful from the minute you enter the hose. From the moment you step inside, you'll be greeted by a beautifully designed space that exudes both elegance and functionality. The main focal point of the kitchen is the exquisite QUARTZ countertops that span throughout the room, offering ample space for meal preparation and entertaining. The sleek and modern design of the countertops adds a touch of sophistication to the heart of the home. The open concept design creates a seamless flow between the living room, dining area, and kitchen, making it ideal for entertaining guests and hosting family gatherings. The master suite is a true sanctuary located on the main floor and features a beautiful bathroom and a large walk in closet. With all the other bedrooms are located upstairs it offers you a private oasis to relax at the end of the day. As you explore the rest of the house, you'll find four spacious bedrooms, providing plenty of room for relaxation and privacy. The master suite is a true sanctuary, The home also features ceramic tile  providing a durable and low-maintenance option that combines style and practicality. The flooring flows seamlessly throughout the living areas, adding a touch of warmth and charm to each room. With its desirable two-story layout, this home offers a great balance of space and functionality. In addition to the interior features, the property conveniently backs up to a conservation area and is partially fenced so you have plenty of privacy. The property is situated in a sought-after location, with convenient access to amenities, schools, beaches, and transportation.  Willow Walk has a beautiful pool and a playground and a park. The neighborhood offers a serene atmosphere, perfect for those seeking a peaceful and comfortable lifestyle. The beautiful beaches of Anna Marie island are a short drive away. You are only a few miles from the Sunshine Skyway bridge and a couple miles from 75.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your own. please use as is contract. All room sizes are approximate.
